&lt;Le Peep Restaurants Inc> said it issuing an Ohio company, charging it copied its restaurant fromits menu to its design.    The action is being taken against &lt;Shelly's Inc>, operatorof three restaurants in Columbus, Ohio, the company said. Thesuit alleges copyright infringement and unfair competition, itsaid.    The suit was filed in U.S. District Court of the SouthernDistrict in Ohio, and seeks damages in excess of 2,250,000, thecompany said. Reuter&#3;